Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.01,Main,Neighbor,0,0,0,,I'm going to go out with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.55,Main,Neighbor,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way! I'll murder you!
