Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.30,Main,Neighbor,0,0,0,,Why, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:53.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この～！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.51,Main,Reigen,0,0,0,,You pervy peeping tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:55.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この陰気な出歯亀が！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.47,Main,Neighbor,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, owie!
