Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:03.31,Main,Reigen,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:06.85,Main,Neighbor,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I was in the wrong! \NI'll never do it again!
