Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:12.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたを好きな気持ちは\N本当に真心なんです！　だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:11.13,Main,Neighbor,0,0,0,,My feelings for you are genuine, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.76,Main,Neighbor,0,0,0,,So, please... p-p-p-p...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:13.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:13.96,Main,Customer 2,0,0,0,,You're seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:18.62,Main,Customer 2,0,0,0,,You're seriously insanely creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:18.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に超キモいわ お前！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ～ 怖がって損したわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:28.08,Main,Customer 2,0,0,0,,I can't believe I was scared of {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:31.74,Main,Reigen,0,0,0,,So he tried to hide his stalking tendencies\Nbehind a supernatural phenomenon.
