Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怪奇現象のせいにしようと\Nしてたんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:33.51,Main,Dimple,0,0,0,,Don't try that at home, Shigeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マネすんなよ 茂夫(しげお)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:34.94,Main,Mob,0,0,0,,Why?
