Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:49.70,Main,Reigen,0,0,0,,All right, let's head back\Nand grab some soba on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:49.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よ～し いったん戻って\N帰り ソバでも食うか？
